               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-51-cd278" type="crimeDate">14th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-51-off277 t18220911-51-cd278"></join>, forty-eight snuff-boxes, value 6 s.; thirty-two bone chessmen, value 6 s. 6 d.; thirty-two ivory chess-men, value 10 s.; twenty-three wood-coloured bones, value 7 s. 8 d.; nine clothes-brushes, value 18 s.; six hat-brushes, value 7 s. 6 d.; seven hair-brushes, value 7 s. 6 d.; five shaving-brushes, value 5 s.; one shaving-box, value 3 d.; two glaziers' diamonds, value 3 s.; seven glass-bead necklaces, value 1 s.; and one duster-brush, value 3 s. 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220911-51-victim539" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Kent
